div.p: Question 1: In 373, the underlined digit (7) is in the tens place.
Question 2: In 1,094, the 9 is in the tens place.
Question 3: In 145,724, the 4 is in the ones place.

ul.li: Place value determines the value of a digit based on its position.
Each position to the left is 10 times greater than the position to its right.
